meta {
  name: Delete Test Group
  type: http
  seq: 5
}

delete {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/siteadmin/test-groups/{{testGroupId}}
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{siteAdminToken}}
}

docs {
  Soft-delete a test group (sets `deletedAt`) **and** cascade soft-delete all its
  lab-test mappings, in one transaction. Auth: SiteAdmin token, requires
  `master-data:write`. 404 `TEST_GROUP_NOT_FOUND` if not a live group.

  After deletion the `groupName` is freed for reuse (the unique index only covers
  active rows), and a subsequent `Get Test Group` returns 404.

  **Sample response — 200**
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "data": {
      "id": "6d0e2f4a-1b2c-4d3e-8f90-a1b2c3d4e5f6",
      "groupName": "Full Body Checkup (Advanced)",
      "createdBy": "a612182e-3038-4d2c-ab1b-b46c43f9d65c",
      "updatedBy": "a612182e-3038-4d2c-ab1b-b46c43f9d65c",
      "createdAt": "2026-07-01T09:00:00.000Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-07-01T09:10:00.000Z",
      "deletedAt": "2026-07-01T09:10:00.000Z"
    },
    "meta": { "timestamp": "2026-07-01T09:10:00.000Z" }
  }
  ```
}
